al cases, and demonstrate the\nsuperior accuracy of the $\\alpha$-stable model to approach the real\nenvironment.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 18 Sep 2017 01:09:58 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 19 Nov 2018 11:56:10 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-11-20"}
