 based on the\nmacroscopic diffusion model and experimental data allow to conclude that the\ncombination of macroscopic and microscopic approach could produce more adequate\nand more accurate description of processes of water vapor interaction with\nporous materials.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 18 Sep 2017 11:55:59 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-09-19"}
