pected than the one of traceroutes. Also in this case our algorithm is\nable to spot periodicities. We argue that some of them are related to\noscillations of the BGP control plane.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 18 Sep 2017 14:21:42 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-09-19"}
