 no apparent correlation\nbetween Rv value and color excess E(B-V) in the range of interest, from 0.2 to\n0.6 mag, or with specific visual extinction per kiloparsec, AV/d.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 18 Sep 2017 14:55:42 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-11-01"}
